question: Give me cooking shows and reality TV shows with an audience score of 7.5.
sql_query1:
SELECT TelevisionShows.Name 
FROM TelevisionShows
WHERE (TelevisionShows.Genre = "Cooking Show" OR TelevisionShows.Genre = "Reality TV Show") AND TelevisionShows.Audience_Score = 7.5
sql_query2:
SELECT TelevisionShows.Name 
FROM TelevisionShows
WHERE TelevisionShows.Genre = "Cooking Show" OR TelevisionShows.Genre = "Reality TV Show" AND TelevisionShows.Audience_Score = 7.5
interpretation1: What cooking shows have an audience score of 7.5 and what reality TV shows have the same score?
interpretation2: List all cooking shows and also list reality TV shows with an audience score of 7.5.
